        "code": "# Web Framework\nfastapi==0.111.0\nuvicorn[standard]==0.29.0\npython-multipart==0.0.9   # UploadFile 처리에 필수\n\n# CV / AI\ntorch==2.3.0\ntorchvision==0.18.0\ntransformers==4.41.0\n\n# 이미지 처리\nPillow==10.3.0\n\n# 유틸리티\npydantic==2.7.1\n"
