      "content": "$ git push -u origin feature/deploy-portfolio\nTo github.com:user/portfolio.git\n * [new branch]      feature/deploy-portfolio -> feature/deploy-portfolio\n\n$ gh pr create --base main --title \"포트폴리오 배포\"\nhttps://github.com/user/portfolio/pull/7\n\n$ npm run build\nvite v5.4.0 building for production...\n✓ 142 modules transformed.\ndist/index.html                   0.46 kB │ gzip:  0.30 kB\ndist/assets/index-a1b2c3d4.css   12.84 kB │ gzip:  3.21 kB\ndist/assets/index-e5f6a7b8.js   168.42 kB │ gzip: 54.10 kB\n✓ built in 3.12s\n\n$ scp -r dist/* ubuntu@13.124.xx.xx:/var/www/html/\nindex.html              100%  471    18.2KB/s   00:00\nindex-e5f6a7b8.js       100%  164KB   2.1MB/s   00:00\n\n--- [EC2 서버 내부] ---\nubuntu@ip-172-31-x:~$ sudo nginx -t\nnginx: configuration file /etc/nginx/nginx.conf test is successful\nubuntu@ip-172-31-x:~$ sudo systemctl restart nginx\n\n$ curl -I http://13.124.xx.xx\nHTTP/1.1 200 OK\nServer: nginx/1.24.0 (Ubuntu)\nContent-Type: text/html\n\n배포 완료 → 브라우저에서 http://13.124.xx.xx 접속 시\n포트폴리오 화면이 표시되고, /projects 새로고침에도 404 없이 정상 동작"
